        <Parent_String>terminals (buildings) [300007748], transportation buildings [300007736], transportation structures [300120693], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
